&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing models to predict resource needs as Stripe demand increases;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working closely with engineers to improve the cost and performance of platforms and services;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employing quantitative methods to drive and automate fleet decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will act as a key strategic data partner to the Core Infrastructure organization at Stripe, and help craft, guide, and drive the strategy and tactics needed to help ensure Stripe can continue to scale with efficiency and dependability as our business rapidly grows.&lt;/p&gt;
