&lt;li data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;10+ years of relevant engineering experience, including 4+ years leading cross-team technical initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
